Speaker 2: Yes, I placed an order days ago, and I haven't received anything yet.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can see where your package is then, sir.

Speaker 2: What's your last name and a zip code?

Speaker 1: My last name is Evertz, and the zip code is 48209.

Speaker 2: Okay, your package will arrive Friday the 13th, sir.

Speaker 1: Okay, Friday the 13th?

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Alrighty. Okay, that's all I needed to know.

Speaker 2: Well, you have a great day now. Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: And you too. Thank you so much.
